metadata.name: Red Gymnocalycium Mihanovichii
metadata.description:
Gymnocalycium mihanovichii is a species of cactus from South America.

This plant is found growing at lower elevations up to 500 meters in Paraguay and northeast Argentina. The species was discovered there in 1903 by Alberto Vojtěch Frič.

This is the first mini cactus I have at home :)
